Length: theme.spaces.fixedMedium)","        }","        .gridMargin(.horizontal)","    }","}","","#Preview {","    InfoCard(","        assetName: \"Picture2\",","        title: \"Orange for the sector\",","        subtitle: \"A complete offer for Institutions\",","        description: \"Our experience as a partner in the digital transformation of companies and institutions guarantees the high efficiency of the services provided.\",","        buttonLabel: \"Transmission\")","        .orangePreview()","}"],"fileName":"InfoCard.swift","fileType":"swift"},"tutorial-onboarding-2-7.png":{"identifier":"tutorial-onboarding-2-7.png","variants":[{"url":"\/images\/OUDSThemesContract\/tutorial-onboarding-2-7.png","traits":["1x","light"]}],"type":"image","alt":"A view with image, texts, button and spacings"},"OUDS-Onboarding-Tutorial.zip":{"type":"download","url":"\/downloads\/OUDSThemesContract\/OUDS-Onboarding-Tutorial.zip","identifier":"OUDS-Onboarding-Tutorial.zip","checksum":"b4526c090a48b401cf3d6bf5035b6a58de1b0786f55523c708b8b0650a3d2d64c5c2b58098805ef2425572fdfb66eed6aa92e69d856445b2793e21d729b5ec05"},"https://www.figma.com/design/zJl6GhY2gMSMAibBJXoNPy/Reveal-and-Onboarding?node-id=2259-4970&m=dev":{"type":"link","title":"the Figma specifications","identifier":"https:\/\/www.figma.com\/design\/zJl6GhY2gMSMAibBJXoNPy\/Reveal-and-Onboarding?node-id=2259-4970&m=dev","titleInlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"the Figma specifications"}],"url":"https:\/\/www.figma.com\/design\/zJl6GhY2gMSMAibBJXoNPy\/Reveal-and-Onboarding?node-id=2259-4970&m=dev"},"doc://OUDSThemesContract/tutorials/OUDSThemesContract/tutorial-onboarding-1-package-and-librairies#Check-Your-Understanding":{"type":"link","titleInlineContent":[{"text":"Check Your Understanding","type":"text"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/tutorials\/OUDSThemesContract\/tutorial-onboarding-1-package-and-librairies#Check-Your-Understanding","url":"\/tutorials\/oudsthemescontract\/tutorial-onboarding-1-package-and-l